        <updateDate>2020-06-09T16:21:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>ALJ Competitive Service Restoration Act</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;makes administrative law judge (ALJ)&nbsp;positions&nbsp;part of the competitive service and&nbsp;otherwise&nbsp;modifies the process for the appointment of ALJs, including by establishing certain minimum qualifications and conditions of employment. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
